      <scopecontent id="aspace_91ea3bb8e870f9d966f081a5aa01b73f">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This finding aid encompasses accessions of single manuscripts and small groups of manuscripts and other papers, by or pertaining to Jean Giono, acquired by the library from a variety of sources. Materials incorporated into the collection prior to January 2000 have been organized into 2 series: <ref xlink:actuate="onRequest" xlink:show="replace" target="ref11">I. Letters</ref>, and <ref xlink:actuate="onRequest" xlink:show="replace" target="ref22">II. Writings</ref>. Materials acquired since that date are listed in <ref xlink:actuate="onRequest" xlink:show="replace" target="ref29">Series III. Additions Since January 2000</ref>.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
